resources.string: Orders above Rs 100 are eligible for free of delivery.
Please share this QR code with the Delivery Boy for the confirmation of your Successful Delivery.
If you do not wish to pay 100% of your total amount then you can pay any percent of total amount between 20% to 100% and rest amount you have to pay once the product is delivered.
Rice is the seed of the grass species Oryza sativa (Asian rice) or Oryza glaberrima (African rice).
